description: Among the various performances in Seoul, "Cat Drum Show" is definitely a special one, as it is the only female percussion group in Korea. After holding its first performance in Seoul in 2006, it became an instant hit, and then officially began a large-scale performance activities, and won awards at various award ceremonies. The performance of "Cat Drum Show" is soft and firm, which can make people appreciate the charm of another Korean woman. The sonorous and powerful drum sound will definitely shock your heart, bringing a passionate audition feast to the audience!

address: 175 Sejong-daero, Sejongno, Jongno-gu, Seoul, South Korea
